    - rid: 107151343762276450
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276451
          - rid: 107151343762276452
          output: "Our followers discover where this \u201Corator\u201D dwells and
            pay him a nocturnal visit. Coincidentally, he does not appear in the
            plaza the following morning, nor any day thereafter.\r\n[Gained 20 Zeal
            & 10 Flock]\r\n"
        - weight: 40
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276453
          output: "What a disaster! Our followers ambush the orator as he concludes
            one of his sermons. Yet, he stands his ground, even as our men begin
            to threaten violence. They clearly misread the situation; the orator\u2019s
            stoicism is enough to rouse his followers to his defense. Our men are
            lynched on the spot.\r\n[Lost 20 Zeal]"
        - weight: 10
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276455
          - rid: 107151343762276456
          - rid: 107151343762276457
          output: "A catastrophe! Matters have spiraled out of control. Our men were
            meant only to give him a fright, but they overplayed their hand and ended
            the poor devil's life! Worse, they did so before the eyes of all his
            followers. Needless to say, our sect\u2019s reputation is left in tatters.\r\n[Lost
            25 Zeal, 10 Bliss & 20 Flock]"
